    <sect1 id="images">
        <title>Images</title>
        <para>
            The image format is png. The image size for the navigation icons is 22x22 pixel.
            All other icons are 16x16 pixel.
        </para>
        <para>
            Images are named onthere function. For example new.png or search.png.
        </para>
        <para>
            Default images are:
        </para>
        <itemizedlist mark="round" >
            <listitem>
                <para>new.png (for creating)</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>search.png (for searching)</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>overview.png (for a overview)</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>logout.png (logout)</para>
